description:
Bartok: The Six String Quartets.

Anyone wishing to investigate 20th century masterworks of the string quartet genre should listen to this. Bartok's Six String Quartets were written in the 30 years between 1909 and 1939. The Takacs Quartet's recordings of these pieces, released by Decca in 1998, are the most magnificent of which I am aware.

Please enjoy.
